        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>When vehicles are operated in a severe service application, the accumulator tube leading from the
                    evaporator may fatigue crack. To remedy this, an accumulator reinforcement kit is available that can
                    be installed without evacuating the air conditioning system.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
